snippet.title: CAT & ONION: A whimsical cat adventure game ✨ Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy CAT & ONION on itch: https://zylinski.itch.io/cat-and-onion or on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2781210/CAT__ONION

CAT & ONION is a warm and whimsical cat adventure where you climb, talk, fly and smack your way to places where no cat has ever gone before!

Go on a short but colossal journey packed with curious characters, imaginative environments and good vibes.
